extends layout1 
block content 
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/styles.css", type="text/css")
    //-  Washbay premise image
    center
      img(src='/images/car wash bay.jpg' alt='' width='800px' height='400px')
    //- jamboron text for pakages main title
    .container
      .jamboron.text-center
        h1(style='font: bolder;')
          strong ZAWASH OFFERS THE BEST CAR WASH PACKAGES AROUND TOWN 
        p
          | At your convinience come and visit our premises and get your car washed by skilled and proffetional car washers. 
          | Zawash can get your car washed at the quickest time posible. Check out packages bellow.
          | Zaabu Washing Bay (ZaWash) is found along Mawanda Road, Kampala. It employs youth in the areas of Kalerwe, Katanga among others. 
          | For more information about booking and access <span> call tel: 0701232323, Email:"zawashbay@gmail.co.ug"
    //-  Small car wash package
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-6.col-md-4
          .card(style='width: 18rem;')
            img.card-img-top(src='/images/sports_car_vector_291850.jpg' alt='...')
            .card-body
              h5.card-title SMALL CAR
              p.card-text
                | Small Car Wash Costs Ten Tousand shillings
                span (10,000/=)
              .btn-group
                button.btn.btn-primary.dropdown-toggle.dropdown-toggle-split(type='button' data-toggle='dropdown' aria-haspopup='true' aria-expanded='false')
                  span.sr-only Toggle Dropdown
                  |                   Details
                .dropdown-menu
                  a.dropdown-item(href='#' style='color: red;') package details
                  p(style='color: blue;')
                    | Under this category a car is considered small if its sitter capacity is 4 passengers and bellow
        //- Boda-Boda wash package
        .col-sm-6.col-md-4
          .card(style='width: 18rem;')
            img.card-img-top(src='/images/bajaj.jpg' alt='...')
            .card-body
              h5.card-title BODA-BODA
              p.card-text
                | Boda-Boda Wash Costs Five Tousand shillings
                span (5,000/=)
              .btn-group
                button.btn.btn-primary.dropdown-toggle.dropdown-toggle-split(type='button' data-toggle='dropdown' aria-haspopup='true' aria-expanded='false')
                  span.sr-only Toggle Dropdown
                  |                   Details
                .dropdown-menu
                  a.dropdown-item(href='#' style='color: red;') Package details
                  p(style='color: blue;') Under this category all mottobikes are considered boda-boda
                  .dropdown-divider
        //-  Medium-size carwash package
        .col-sm-6.col-md-4
          .card(style='width: 18rem;')
            img.card-img-top(src='/images/taxi.jpg' alt='...')
            .card-body
              h5.card-title MEDIUM CARS
              p.card-text
                | Medium Car Wash Costs Fifteen Tousand shillings
                span (15,000/=)
              .btn-group
                button.btn.btn-primary.dropdown-toggle.dropdown-toggle-split(type='button' data-toggle='dropdown' aria-haspopup='true' aria-expanded='false')
                  span.sr-only Toggle Dropdown
                  |                   Details
                .dropdown-menu
                  a.dropdown-item(href='#' style='color: red;') Package details
                  p(style='color: blue;')
                    | Under this category sitter capacity is considered,this include any car with sitter capacity beyond 4 passengers
                  .dropdown-divider
        //-  Engine wash package
        .container
          .row
            .col-sm-6.col-md-4
              .card(style='width: 18rem;')
                img.card-img-top(src='/images/engine.jpg' alt='...')
                .card-body
                  h5.card-title ENGINE
                  p.card-text
                    | Engine Wash Costs Ten Tousand shillings
                    span (10,000/=)
                  .btn-group
                    button.btn.btn-primary.dropdown-toggle.dropdown-toggle-split(type='button' data-toggle='dropdown' aria-haspopup='true' aria-expanded='false')
                      span.sr-only Toggle Dropdown
                      |                       Details
                    .dropdown-menu
                      a.dropdown-item(href='#' style='color: red;') Package details
                      p(style='color:blue;')
                        | All vihecle engines are categorized in this package,whether small,medium,big or motorbikes
                      .dropdown-divider
            //- zawash image illustration
            .col-sm-6.col-md-4
              img(src='/images/wash cartoon.jpg' alt='' width='350' height='300')
            //- // fullwash pakage card
            .col-sm-6.col-md-4
              .card(style='width: 18rem;')
                img.card-img-top(src='/images/full wash.jpg' alt='...')
                .card-body
                  h5.card-title FULL WASH
                  p.card-text
                    | A Full Wash Costs Twenty Tousand shillings
                    span (20,000/=)
                .button
                  .btn-group
                    button.btn.btn-primary.dropdown-toggle(type='button' data-toggle='dropdown' aria-haspopup='true' aria-expanded='false')
                      | Details
                    .dropdown-menu
                      a.dropdown-item(href='#' style='color: red;') Package details
                      p(style='color: blue;')
                        | Under this category vehecles or motorbikes are washed in full including external and internal parts e.g engine
                      .dropdown-divider
      //- demonstration images during work hours
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-6
            img(src='/images/washing team2.png' alt='' width='500' height='300')
          .col-md-5
            img(src='/images/wash1.png' alt='' width='500' height='300')
      br
      br
      //-footer Copyright message
      footer.bg-light.text-center.text-lg-start
        .text-center.p-3(style='background-color: black;')
          | Copyright &copy; 2021 Zawash Car Bay.All rights reserved,Developed by Malinga Robert
      script(src='css/jquery-3.6.0.js')
      script(src='css/bootstrap-4.6.0-dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.js')
